00:19:57,960 --> 00:20:00,160
You're going out to eat dressed in

379
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:02,519
this?

380
00:20:03,079 --> 00:20:05,799
What's wrong? Do you think it's not suitable?

381
00:20:05,799 --> 00:20:08,319
It's just

382
00:20:08,319 --> 00:20:10,319
a little plain.

383
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:14,119
Then I'll change into something else.

384
00:20:14,119 --> 00:20:16,039
How quickly time passes.

385
00:20:16,039 --> 00:20:17,279
Last time I saw Jiajia,

386
00:20:17,279 --> 00:20:18,680
she was just a junior in college.

387
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:21,799
Now she's bringing her boyfriend
to meet the parents.

388
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:24,440
I even brought a gift for Jiajia.

389
00:20:24,440 --> 00:20:27,160
When do you think
is the right time to give it to her?

390
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:31,000
Hello, okay. I'll come down right away.

391
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:32,960
She just got a boyfriend.

392
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,680
Don't take it that seriously.

393
00:20:34,680 --> 00:20:37,279
What happens in the future is still uncertain.

394
00:20:37,279 --> 00:20:40,559
Alright, Jiajia is here.
I'm going down first, you hurry up.

395
00:20:40,559 --> 00:20:43,519
I'm not ready yet, just wait for me.

396
00:20:56,400 --> 00:20:58,960
- Jiajia.
- Mom.

397
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,799
I'll do it myself, thank you.

398
00:21:00,799 --> 00:21:02,079
Did you rest well?

399
00:21:02,079 --> 00:21:03,759
Very well.

400
00:21:03,759 --> 00:21:06,440
Over there, Dad, Ms. Meng.

401
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:08,456
This way.

402
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,160
How should we sit?

403
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:13,192
Mom, sit here.

404
00:21:14,359 --> 00:21:16,759
Dad, Ms. Meng.

405
00:21:18,079 --> 00:21:19,720
Well, Jiajia.

406
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:21,920
Sit between me and your mom.

