412
00:21:41,559 --> 00:21:42,839
No, Dad.

413
00:21:42,839 --> 00:21:45,119
He took leave to pick you up,

414
00:21:45,119 --> 00:21:46,759
but something came up at the last minute

415
00:21:46,759 --> 00:21:48,359
and he really couldn't come.

416
00:21:48,359 --> 00:21:49,960
He's probably still busy right now,

417
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:51,359
should be arriving soon.

418
00:21:51,359 --> 00:21:52,839
He will be here soon.

419
00:21:52,839 --> 00:21:54,599
Xu, are you in such a hurry?

420
00:21:54,599 --> 00:21:55,599
Now that we're here,

421
00:21:55,599 --> 00:21:57,720
