422
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,599
Then, waitress, bring me the menu.

423
00:22:02,599 --> 00:22:04,960
I'll order some dishes first.

424
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:07,240
Mr. Xu has already
ordered the dishes for today.

425
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:10,079
If needed, we can serve the dishes at any time.

426
00:22:10,079 --> 00:22:13,839
- Mr. Xu?
- Hao.

427
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:18,000
Then what did he order?

428
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:21,079
- What did he order? Let me take a look.
- This is the menu.

429
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:25,759
- I won't disturb you anymore.
- Dad is still the same,

430
00:22:25,759 --> 00:22:27,960
acting like a scholar.

431
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:29,359
Being meticulous in everything.

432
00:22:29,359 --> 00:22:31,599
He's been this way since his youth.

433
00:22:31,599 --> 00:22:34,640
So boring.

434
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:36,000
Sorry, sorry.

435
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,240
Sorry I'm late.

436
00:22:37,240 --> 00:22:39,880
Really sorry, Aunt.

437
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:42,160
Xu Junhao.

438
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:44,119
Just call me Hao.

439
00:22:44,119 --> 00:22:45,799
Hao.

440
00:22:45,799 --> 00:22:48,440
Jiajia, you didn't tell me
