450
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:24,559
I sincerely apologize to you. I'm sorry.

451
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:36,960
Xu, is the menu that funny?

452
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:39,000
Greet him.

453
00:23:49,359 --> 00:23:52,440
- Waitress.
- Waitress, come on.

454
00:24:04,039 --> 00:24:07,480
Uncle, nice to meet you.

455
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:09,880
Tired of standing? Have a seat.

456
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,880
Take a seat.

457
00:24:20,039 --> 00:24:23,160
Well, your surname is Xu, right?

458
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:24,680
- Yes.
- Then I'll call you Xu.

459
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:26,480
That's fine.

460
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:29,160
What do you do for work?

461
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,720
Actually, I am in charge of

462
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:32,039
this hotel management.

463
00:24:32,039 --> 00:24:36,559
For entertainment, public relations,
or any aspect, I'm in charge.

464
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,279
Your Mandarin is quite good.

465
00:24:39,279 --> 00:24:40,480
Thank you.

466
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:42,519
How many people in your household?

467
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,039
How many people are there in your family?

468
00:24:46,039 --> 00:24:48,799
Well, apart from my parents,

469
00:24:48,799 --> 00:24:50,119
I am the eldest son,

470
00:24:50,119 --> 00:24:51,920
and I have a younger brother,

471
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:52,920
who has just entered society

472
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:54,240
and has started working.

473
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:59,039
And I have a sister
who just started sixth grade.

474
00:24:59,039 --> 00:25:01,000
What do your parents do?

475
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:02,759
When my parents were young,

476
00:25:02,759 --> 00:25:04,559
