478
00:25:06,559 --> 00:25:08,799
Now in Macau, it is somewhat

479
00:25:08,799 --> 00:25:11,119
renowned.

480
00:25:11,119 --> 00:25:13,880
Are you still living with your parents now?

481
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:14,960
Uncle, don't be kidding.

482
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:15,960
I have moved out a long time ago.

483
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:18,160
I rented a house.

484
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,759
That means

485
00:25:19,759 --> 00:25:22,119
