486
00:25:22,119 --> 00:25:24,640
If getting married, I would buy a house.

487
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:28,000
Wherever Jiajia likes to live,
that's where I will buy.

488
00:25:32,119 --> 00:25:33,480
That easy?

489
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:35,599
You are young, yet not modest at all.

490
00:25:35,599 --> 00:25:37,200
Uncle, I am not that young anymore.

491
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,920
I am already thirty-seven.

492
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:39,960
Actually, I know

493
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,400
that many people say

494
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:44,920
that marriage is not about money,
just being in love is enough.

495
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:46,440
But I know

496
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:48,839
that Jiajia is your precious one.

497
00:25:48,839 --> 00:25:49,960
If she is with me,

498
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:52,279
she should not suffer.

499
00:25:52,279 --> 00:25:57,160
Anyone can say sweet words.

500
00:25:57,160 --> 00:26:00,119
But it may not be the case
when it comes to the real thing.

501
00:26:03,079 --> 00:26:04,319
Xu, you are here in Macau

502
00:26:04,319 --> 00:26:05,880
to check on his family background?

503
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:08,200
- No, no.
- Hao, don't take it to heart.

504
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:09,319
Jiajia's dad

505
00:26:09,319 --> 00:26:11,319
is always like this,

506
00:26:11,319 --> 00:26:12,640
having been

507
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,359
a teacher all his life.

508
00:26:14,359 --> 00:26:16,400
He's quite

509
00:26:18,319 --> 00:26:19,920
serious.

510
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:22,480
No, not serious at all.

511
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,960
If I had such a beautiful

512
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,359
and outstanding daughter

513
00:26:25,359 --> 00:26:26,440
like Jiajia,

514
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:27,440
I would ask the same.

515
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:30,319
It's quite normal, right?

516
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:34,680
- A senior manager…
- No.

517
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:38,640
