520
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:45,480
Let's serve the dishes.

521
00:26:46,319 --> 00:26:48,000
Come on, let's eat.

522
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:51,599
- Waitress, serve the dishes.
- Alright.

523
00:26:55,319 --> 00:26:57,384
Hurry up.

524
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:13,000
This is our hotel's specialty dish,

525
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,400
Yuan Yang mixed rice.

526
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:15,599
Please enjoy.

527
00:27:15,599 --> 00:27:18,119
- Yuan Yang mixed rice.
- Right.

528
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:23,240
Eat up.

529
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:27,640
Uncle, are you feeling unwell?

530
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,640
The weather in Macau

531
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:30,160
