532
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,519
Too humid, right?

533
00:27:31,519 --> 00:27:33,920
If you need a dehumidifier

534
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:35,872
or aromatherapy, or you don't like the pillow,

535
00:27:35,872 --> 00:27:38,119
you can tell me.

536
00:27:38,119 --> 00:27:39,559
No. I'm from Shanghai,

537
00:27:39,559 --> 00:27:42,519
so I'm pretty used to it.

538
00:27:42,519 --> 00:27:44,240
Don't overthink it.

539
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,319
We are here

540
00:27:45,319 --> 00:27:47,519
to come see you,

541
00:27:47,519 --> 00:27:49,680
and also visit Macau.

542
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:51,480
Macau is really nice for travel.

543
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,960
Actually, Macau has a lot

544
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:55,640
of sightseeing spots and scenery

545
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:57,079
that you can explore.

546
00:27:57,079 --> 00:27:58,519
Like Macau Tower.

547
00:27:58,519 --> 00:27:59,799
The Macau Tower is great.

548
00:27:59,799 --> 00:28:01,000
It's romantic to go there at night.

549
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:03,400
You can overlook
the entire night view of Macau,

550
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:05,400
which I really like.

551
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:10,119
- And the world-famous bungee jump.
- What?

552
00:28:10,119 --> 00:28:12,136
Bungee jump.

